<h1 class="glow">QUESTION TIME.</h1>
<br>
<div class="glowsmall"><center>
  <br>
 <a href="/projects" title="Projects">Projects</a> | <a href="/about2" title="About">About</a> | <a href="/contact" title="Contact">Contact</a> | <a href="/logout" title="Logout">Logout</a><br>
</center></div><br>
<center class="glowsmall"><br>
CONSIDER YOUR TASK AND ANSWER THE QUESTIONS BELOW...<br>
</center>
<h2 class="glowblue"><%= @task.the_action_description %></h2>
<br>
<br>

<form class="" action="/phase_2_question_time/<%=@project.id%>/<%=@task.id%>/<%=@task_score.id%>" method="post">
  <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="patch">
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th><center>how fast can you get this done?</center></th>
      <th><center>how much effort might this take?</center></th>
      <th><center>how important is it?</center></th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    <td>
      <input type="hidden" name="quick_or_slow_for_form_rendering" value="<%= @task_score.quick_or_slow_for_form_rendering%>">
      <INPUT type="radio" name="quick_or_slow_for_form_rendering" value="quick"> I can do this quickly!<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="quick_or_slow_for_form_rendering" value="slow"> This could take a while.<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="quick_or_slow_for_form_rendering" value="uncertain"> I'm not sure.<br><br>
    </td>
    <td>
      <input type="hidden" name="easy_or_hard_for_form_rendering" value="<%=@task_score.easy_or_hard_for_form_rendering%>">
      <INPUT type="radio" name="easy_or_hard_for_form_rendering" value="easy"> This is probably easy.<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="easy_or_hard_for_form_rendering" value="difficult"> This may be difficult.<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="easy_or_hard_for_form_rendering" value="uncertain"> It's hard to say.<br><br>
    </td>
    <td>
      <input type="hidden" name="necessary_or_optional_for_form_rendering" value="<%= @task_score.necessary_or_optional_for_form_rendering %>">
      <INPUT type="radio" name="necessary_or_optional_for_form_rendering" value="necessary"> This is absolutely necessary.<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="necessary_or_optional_for_form_rendering" value="optional"> It would be nice if there's time.<br><br>
      <INPUT type="radio" name="necessary_or_optional_for_form_rendering" value="uncertain"> I can't tell.<br><br>
    </td>
  </table>
  <center>
    <br>
  <input type="submit" value="LET'S CONTINUE."></center>
</form>
<br>
